<tr>
<td>
<p class="subtitle">The South Yorkshire Steel 
Industry and the Industrial Revolution -
<span style="font-weight: 400"><font size="2">David 
Hey, University of Sheffield</font></span></td>
<td width="101" align="right">
<b><span style="font-size: 8pt">
<a href="../UKreading-index.asp">
<img border="0" src="../../00-100-globIncl/intNavImg/arrowBack.jpg" width="24" height="24"></a> 
1 of 3 <a href="sYorshireSteel2.asp">
<img border="0" src="../../00-100-globIncl/intNavImg/arrowNext.jpg" width="24" height="24"></a></span></b></td>
</tr>
